1. *Toni* se vratio u školu. (Toni returned to school.)
2. Ona je sada srećna što je ponovo s *Tonom*. (She is now happy to be with Toni again.)
3. *Toni* je nedavno dobio novi posao. (Toni recently got a new job.)
4. Njegovi roditelji su srećni što je *Toni* uspeo. (His parents are happy that Toni succeeded.)
5. *Toniju* je potrebna pomoć pri rešavanju zadatka. (Toni needs help with solving the task.)
6. Njegova sestra je sada zadovoljna što je *Toni* uspešan. (His sister is now satisfied that Toni is successful.)